304bba4b325b1376f836b16f453d7","tid":1022102,"uid":204659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"由A畫一條垂直線去VB,C畫一條垂直線去VB<br />\n求哂2條線長度,<br />\n最後用cos law計夾角"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"錯concept，兩條垂高唔相交於VB上嘅一點"},{"pid":"791ba0ab615eb3f24378d3eecad7fc442f2b0729","tid":1022102,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f49e445c105304bba4b325b1376f836b16f453d7","tid":1022102,"uid":204659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"由A畫一條垂直線去VB,C畫一條垂直線去VB<br />\n求哂2條線長度,<br />\n最後用cos law計夾角"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T19:59:01.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"22e5449832f6f7db327250d70e8c251611bbfcc5","tid":1022102,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d98a83f35f6d51439ba91a3c2a435670d1d23244","tid":1022102,"uid":148589,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f49e445c105304bba4b325b1376f836b16f453d7","tid":1022102,"uid":204659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"由A畫一條垂直線去VB,C畫一條垂直線去VB<br />\n求哂2條線長度,<br />\n最後用cos law計夾角"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"錯concept，兩條垂高唔相交於VB上嘅一點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T00:47:28.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n穿A果條同穿C果條線分別垂直拉落VB<br />\n2點唔會重疊<br />\n因為2個3角形都唔同大細"},{"pid":"80874045760122ae9348025d3f4772524d1ded14","tid":1022102,"uid":204659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d98a83f35f6d51439ba91a3c2a435670d1d23244","tid":1022102,"uid":148589,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f49e445c105304bba4b325b1376f836b16f453d7","tid":1022102,"uid":204659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"由A畫一條垂直線去VB,C畫一條垂直線去VB<br />\n求哂2條線長度,<br />\n最後用cos law計夾角"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"錯concept，兩條垂高唔相交於VB上嘅一點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T02:47:52.000Z","msg":"係我中伏<br />\n樓主唔好聽我講，sorry"},{"p