ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783ab5612c45f5d244d1c34daa2a032c957f114f","tid":1022102,"uid":15595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"ABV切一半係直角三角形<br />\n<br />\n用VB做底你會搵到A&rsquo;BV既高 <br />\n嗰點就係你要既野<br />\nCommon side VB短邊 底邊 夾角 搵到最後一條線<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"414befdbe0b866826bfc2796bc39e53faef2ac69","tid":1022102,"uid":15595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"783ab5612c45f5d244d1c34daa2a032c957f114f","tid":1022102,"uid":15595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"ABV切一半係直角三角形<br />\n<br />\n用VB做底你會搵到A&rsquo;BV既高 <br />\n嗰點就係你要既野<br />\nCommon side VB短邊 底邊 夾角 搵到最後一條線<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"當我無講過 好似未做完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e5e61fa07c3932cd2e4b7825fc009ee9208f92","tid":1022102,"uid":148589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"唔得閒寫，講個step點做算<br />\n<br />\nVBC:<br />\n搵由C去VB個垂高，隻腳叫求其Let做H<br />\n<br />\nVAB:<br />\n搵由H拉條垂直於VB嘅線出去，拉到去AB之間一點（唔係中點黎），求其Let做K<br />\n<br />\n以上CH同HK用最普通sin cos tan 或者畢氏定理都搵到<br />\n<br />\n跟住用底個長方形搵CK（要計左BK先，再用畢氏定理）<br />\n<br />\n最後，角CHK 就係題目要嘅個隻角（用cosine law）"},{"pid":"f5dd7a941b0d0fc9c85d1232291d281419ab955e","tid":1022102,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52e5e61fa07c3932cd2e4b7825fc009ee9208f92","tid":1022102,"uid":148589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"唔得閒寫，講個step點做算<br />\n<br />\nVBC:<br />\n搵由C去VB個垂高，隻腳叫求其Let做H<br />\n<br />\nVAB:<br />\n搵由H拉條垂直於VB嘅線出去，拉到去AB之間一點（唔係中點黎），求其Let做K<br />\n<br />\n以上CH同HK用最普通sin cos tan 或者畢氏定理都搵到<br />\n<br />\n跟住用底個長方形搵CK（要計左BK先，再用畢氏定理）<br />\n<br />\n最後，角CHK 就係題目要嘅個隻角（用cosine law）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}